{"tid":2205132,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"「iPhone SE Plus」保護貼現身購物網站：或明年下半年發佈","createTime":"2020-09-16T14:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T01:30:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5acc642ba96b5ac01b57295a37a99fa86fe3a008","tid":2205132,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://feng-bbs-att-1255531212.image.myqcloud.com/2020/09/16/052208rzh9su07kh3k3r0j.jpg?imageMogr2/format/jpg/interlace/0/quality/100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffeng-bbs-att-1255531212.image.myqcloud.com%2F2020%2F09%2F16%2F052208rzh9su07kh3k3r0j.jpg%3FimageMogr2%2Fformat%2Fjpg%2Finterlace%2F0%2Fquality%2F100&h=c48d912f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在今天凌晨的發佈會舉行之前，有 Reddit 用戶發現，百思買在其網站上列出了未發佈的「iPhone SE Plus 2020」的屏幕保護膜。值得一提的是，該屏幕保護膜也被列為與 iPhone 6 Plus，iPhone 7 Plus 和 iPhone 8 Plus 兼容。<br />\nimage<br />\n屏幕保護膜來自百思買本身擁有的 Insignia 品牌。儘管之前就有傳言稱 iPhone SE Plus 將於 2021 年下半年發佈，但百思買目前不太可能會獲得有關此新設備的任何信息，該網頁可能是一個佔位符，又可能是一次錯誤的操作。<br />\n<br />\n根據之前的消息，<span class=\"brown\">iPhone SE Plus 將在側面電源按鈕中內置 Touch ID</span>，這和今天發佈的 iPad Air 類似。該設備將採用 5.5 英吋或 6.1 英吋的顯示屏，不支持面容 ID。<br />\n<br />\n至於這款設備何時發佈，目前尚未有進一步的消息。"},{"pid":"2beb84b6af4be50acd164b00bf0f980f9fdf2e43","tid":2205132,"uid":340623,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"又撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a68e01f8ce15d5feeac27a425f7b9afc8bc64c","tid":2205132,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2beb84b6af4be50acd164b00bf0f980f9fdf2e43","tid":2205132,"uid":340623,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"又撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"無face id，應該會縮小咗個m字額"},{"pid":"0bf6c4a871cdc9a620f12c3de85239d46d47de50","tid":2205132,"uid":22675,"like":0,"